channel.title: Eating help
channel.description: Ok.. This is kinda weird. On my server the max levels are 150. Lets say your hitpoints are 99/150 and you eat a manta ray, now you have 124hits. You eat another manta ray, and your HP doesn't go back up.. This happens to me for every number over 100. Say ur Hp is 76.. you eat a manta and you have 101. You eat again, and it stays 101.. Anyone know how to fix this? Manta's wont heal you if your Hits are over 100.
